window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>I never thought I would date a dragon, or feed him chicken strips late at night, but life has gotten interesting.</p> <p>My steady dragon - you may know him as Lord Zavryd’nokquetal, but I get to call him Zav - is offering to take me to the elven homeland to meet my father and learn to harness the magic in my blood.</p> <p>Sure, I’m wary about his plans to <i>f</i>orce the elves to train me, but I need every advantage I can get. Especially when vampire attacks start cropping up all over Seattle, and my friend and business partner, Dimitri, disappears.</p> <p>Unfortunately, my training will have to wait. If I don’t find my friend in time, I may never see him alive again.</p>"; 
